The paper focuses on improving sample efficiency in deep reinforcement learning using action guidance from a non-expert demonstrator in a multi-agent domain. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), game theory (cs.GT), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), and robotics (cs.RO). However, since the paper primarily deals with deep reinforcement learning, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories.
